    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，根节点用圆形样式突出产品定位。那主干分支您希望按什么维度划分？比如功能模块还是用户场景？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "root style"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "按功能模块来。我想到四个核心方向：Task Management、Collaboration、Reporting，还有Integrations。每个下面再展开具体功能点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Task Management",
        "Collaboration",
        "Reporting",
        "Integrations"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，四个主干分支已建好。Task Management这边我先放「创建和分配任务」「截止日期提醒」「子任务清单」，还有一个「拖拽调整优先级」——这个交互挺关键的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Task Management",
        "Create and assign tasks",
        "Due dates and reminders",
        "Subtask checklists",
        "Drag-and-drop priority"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，拖拽排序是亮点。Collaboration这块需要强调实时性——「实时评论」「@提及通知」「文件附件」，再加个「活动动态」让用户感知团队进展。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Collaboration",
        "Real-time comments",
        "@mentions and notifications",
        "File attachments",
        "Activity feed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Collaboration的四个叶子节点已添加。Reporting这边我打算放「燃尽图」「速度跟踪」，还有「导出PDF」方便分享，您看够吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reporting",
        "Burndown charts",
        "Velocity tracking",
        "Export to PDF"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "够了，Reporting保持简洁。最后Integrations必须打通外部工具——「Slack通知」「GitHub issue同步」「日历同步」，这三项是用户高频诉求。",
      "elements_involved": [
